These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, pepperade
There 2 different types of food: apple, pepper
1. the person drinking pepperade is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person drinking pepperade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | pepperade  | water |
| Food       | apple | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | cola | fanta |
| Sport      | rowing     | rugby  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, zombie
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, japanese
1. the russian is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the russian is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | zombie  |
| Nationality   | russian | japanese |

 #################################

 
