.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, entrepreneur
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | drawing | magic-tricks |
| Job     | firefighter        | entrepreneur |

